-- ds.page.body:

We have developed the `signup-form-popup` component for [admint.io](https://admint.io/), 
which matches the design currently displayed on the live site.

-- ds.h3: How to use?

To use `signup-form-popup` component you need to `import` `lib` inside your
`.ftd` file

-- ds.code:
lang: ftd


\-- import: fifthtry.github.io/admint.io/lib

-- ds.markdown:

Once you import `lib` inside your `.ftd` file, use the `signup-form-popup`
component by adding all required attributes of it. Also, add global mutable
variable `show-signup-popup` inside your `.ftd` file and pass it to `$visible:`
attribute as shown in below code snippet:

-- ds.rendered:

-- ds.rendered.input:

\-- boolean $show-signup-popup: false

\-- lib.signup-form-popup: Join the waitlist to get updated when we go live!
name-label: Name
identity-label: Who are you?
org-label: Organization Name
email-label: Email id
cta-text: Join waitlist
$visible: $show-signup-popup

-- ds.rendered.output:

-- end: ds.rendered.output

-- end: ds.rendered

